This paper deals with audio-visual scene-aware dialog, which involves processing video features of multiple modalities, including text, visual, and audio features. Therefore, it is likely to belong to the categories of natural language processing (cs.CL), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), machine learning (cs.LG), and multimedia (cs.MM).
